parameters: \N<Segi>What... is this?
\N<Segi>You want me to change into this...? But... this is...
air04

\N<Customer>Hey... are you sure this is okay? Is Segi really going to
come here...?
\N<Shopkeeper>Yeah, no mistake about it. That's the deal.
\N<Customer>...And yet you're making us wait quite a bit.

\N<Shopkeeper>She probably needs time to prepare herself. After all, even
though she's in disguise, she's going to be exposing her
skin openly to men other than her husband.
\N<Customer>Hey... don't push from behind! It's cramped in here!

\N<Customer>Shut up...! I can't see well from here! And she's not coming
at all...!

\N<Customer>Like I care. If you're so concerned, then cough up more
money like me...!
\N<Customer>What did you say...!?
\N<Shopkeeper>Haha, stop fighting. Don't worry, she'll surely appear soon.

The small room was stifling with the men's body heat. Amidst
it, they were whispering and discussing something.

\N<Customer>Hey, hey... we've been waiting quite a while...? Is it
really okay?
\N<Customer>...Be quiet. I hear something...
\N<Customer>Really... Segi...! Segi has come...!

\N<Customer>Ha, haha... Can you believe it!? Is this even possible!? On
the other side of that mirror, Segi is going to change
clothes...!?
\N<Customer>Ahh!!??

In front of the excited men, the image of Segi with a
melancholic expression appeared before a large mirror.
\N<Customer>She's here! She really came...!

Contrary to the men's joy and anticipation, Segi's
expression on the other side of the mirror was gloomy. And
there was no sign that she realized she was being exposed to
curious eyes through the trick mirror.
\N<Customer>Ha... Ahh!?
\N<Customer>Hey, hey! What's going on!? I can't see well at all!

The sound of Segi touching her clothes could be heard from
the other side of the mirror. However, the trick mirror
remained fogged up. This would hardly satisfy the men's
desires.

\N<Customer>We can see her, but this is just torture! Shopkeeper, what's
going on here!? Hey!

\N<Customer>Hey! It's a waste if Segi is undressing right in front of us
and we can't see it! What's happening!?

\N<Shopkeeper>This is... unexpected. Unlucky, it seems like a malfunction
of the equipment.

\N<Customer>Don't mess with us! Unlucky!? We paid money for this!? Is a
malfunction an excuse!?

\N<Shopkeeper>Alright, alright. I'll make sure it's fixed by next time.
And I'll make it free for you then.
\N<Customer>Next time!? Is there definitely going to be a next time!?
\N<Shopkeeper>Yes, I promise.

\N<Customer>Tch... damn it! Getting our hopes up for nothing...! Listen
up...! Make sure you fix the malfunction by next time...!

\N<Shopkeeper>Haha, don't be so impatient. Surely she will come again
soon...
\N<Customer>Really? Are you sure? How can you be so certain?

\N<Shopkeeper>This is a tavern. Given the nature of this place, various
stories come to my ears. Including those from the Luda
folks.
\N<Customer>...?

\N<Shopkeeper>She'll definitely come again. So you guys should keep coming
to the shop frequently and spend your money, alright?
\N<Customer>You're greedy... but I'll trust you this time.
\N<Shopkeeper>Yeah... look forward to it.
